metadata.name: somewhere in between.
metadata.description:
when we got lost..

HIGH FEVER, 

we took a walk,

i think i saw tomorrow.

i hear colours,

i see sound.

how did we get here? 

all i ever need.

HIGH FEVER,

wont you walk with me?

*****

"high fever" is a three part series,  

the collection focuses on using 35mm film as a resource, 
yet adapting and experimenting with other analog procedures.

thank you, i love you.
